&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Honor Commitments, Your Word Matters&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; - Specific, Measurable, Attainable, Relevant &amp;amp; Timely (S.M.A.R.T) Asks &amp;amp; Answers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
